main event: A witness spotted a saucer-shaped UFO on the road in Sparks, Georgia on November 28, 1966.
interesting points: The UFO was described as looking like two saucers inverted on top of each other, with a smooth surface and no protrusions.
The UFO was estimated to be as large as a semi-truck in width and 18-19 feet in height.
The UFO was silver in color and had one flashing red light and several glowing white lights.
The witness reported that the car radio began buzzing as the UFO approached.

that were reflective like cat eyes as the UFO took off from the road.
